+//! number that 0.7.2 PR-2 will use to re-derive `AC013B_RECALL_FLOOR`
+//! as `R - 2*sigma`.
+//!
+//! ## Recall posture (AC-075, 0.8.0 Slice 40 / GA-2 — eu7 is the verdict)
