# wheel `release.yml`'s build-python job emits to PyPI. So a plain
# `pip install -e 'src/python[dev]'` has NO hook surface. The few tests that
# need it carry `@pytest.mark.requires_test_hooks`; `tests/conftest.py` may
# rebuild the binding with
